__ Cantrip: Spook ____________________________ Cost: 15 ______________________

Use:  cantrip spook                            Material Component: creature
Use:  C spook

The cantrip spook is a minor magic of the sphere of illusion.  When intoned,
the caster can cause a relatively small or inexperienced creature to 
experience such unmigitigated terror that they flee the room as quickly as
possible.  Great fun to use on Harry or other such annoyances. 
